  <brief_title>RIPC and Platelet Activation on Platelet Activation During Cardiopulmonary Bypass</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Remote Ischemic Preconditioning on Platelet Activation During Cardiac Surgery With Cardiopulmonary Bypass</official_title>
